rComments: Moriarity is great in regards to everything except for his exams. There was an open-book exam for both midterm and the final. They were MC and had only 20-30 questions for a 2-3 hour exam. Each question was 1 page and answers were always a) I, II, III b) all of the above, etc. One of his questions was wrong according to the WHO and he refused this.
